```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
# set the correct assay.
alldata@active.assay = "CCA"

alldata <- FindNeighbors(alldata, dims = 1:30, k.param = 60, prune.SNN = 1/15)

# check the names for graphs in the object.
names(alldata@graphs)
```

